						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">unregistered wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">ok..  in <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=5770&amp;start=0" class="postlink">this thread</a> Bregalad helped me learn that a 16x16 pixel image is a meta-sprite.  So are the ghosts, in nes pacman, meta-sprites?</div>
<br />Yes, almost any game sprite-object is a metasprite due to the 8x8 or 8x16 limitation of the hardware sprites on the nes.</div>

